{"type": "article", "id": 25248, "title": "黑白搭配的酒精饮料包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-11T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104127GyD7bVRZxzvaPoiH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款酒的包装外加了一层黑色的丝网，就增加了一层年轻和现代的色彩。酒瓶上的包装也采用黑白搭配的形式，依然可以透过菱形网格看到 Cuarentona 的名字，简洁时尚。这种来自西班牙的饮料加入了草药、香料以及经过 40 天干燥的甜茴香，所以在木质瓶盖上写出了 +40 的标注。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071041233P6IVRj5M1UzvCig.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24814815\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104125hLzj7VCdbDUlm85t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104126phqUKN65MaegVHcS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104126UKx23QiBlshtMAGD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 250px; width: 375px; left: 417px; top: 1019px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104127kzGcxoTyXJ6pBSqi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}